  "title": "Anatomica: A Comedy About Meat, Bones, & The Skin You're In",
  "description": "WHAT IS THE BEST TYPE OF SKELETON? This hilarious, captivating &amp; sometimes-unsettling solo comedy questions everything about the body. Part stand-up &amp; part storytelling, ANATOMICA is a gloriously deranged Ted-Talk by a wanna-be scientist who dropped out of college to go to clown school. ★★★★★ - The Edmonton Journal 2023 Holdover",
  "credits": "<strong>Playwright</strong>: Amica Hunter<br/><strong>Cast</strong>: Amica Hunter<br/>",
  "website": "https://amicahunter.com | https://instagram.com/meatymeekers",
  "plain_language": "ANATOMICA is a show about an artist exploring what it feels like to live in a body. They look at different animal skeletons and share personal stories to find out which skeleton might be the most comfortable.",
